to a recycled compound that can then be reused in rubber products. Like shoe soles that provide all the traction and durability.
  • ReCanva fabric used in our footwear is made with 100% recycled PET that delivers durability and breathability. It looks and feels just like traditional cotton canvas and carries with it all of the same attributes that traditional canvas is known for.

    • Footwear Care

    Gently dust these sneakers with a soft-bristled shoe brush.
